         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Dear friend, ¶  ¶  ¶ I am sending you Barbados cotton, a few seeds, and ordinary Gossypium arboreum in larger quantity. I hope you are quite well with your dear family. — Excuse my haste. ¶  ¶ — ¶  ¶ ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">57.08.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Friedrich Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M was made Director of the Melbourne Botanic Gardens on 13 August 1857; the letter is dated to August 1857 on the basis of M's comment,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am now formally installed...'.</p>
               </note>[August 1857]</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Lieber Freund.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich sende Dir Barbados Baumwolle ein paar Samen u gewöhnl Gossyp arboreum in grösserer Menge. Ich hoffe Du bist ganz Wohl mit Deiner lieben Familie. — Entschuldige meine Eile. — Ich bin jetzt formell installirt als<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Director</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>des bot Gartens; u will alles mögliche thun, den Garten in die Höhe zu bringen u die jetzt existirenden 1500 Pfl. in 2 Jahren zu 5000 zu vermehren Bitte ja sende mir doch eine gute Sammlung euerer Scrub Samen Die jungen Herren Fischer können vielleicht auch ein wenig dazu beitragen. Es wird in meiner Macht liegen, eine grosse Gegengabe zu machen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit treuer Freundschaft</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear friend,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am sending you Barbados cotton, a few seeds, and ordinary Gossypium arboreum in larger quantity. I hope you are quite well with your dear family. — Excuse my haste.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am now formally installed as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Director</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of the Botanic Garden and want to do all kinds of things to upgrade the Garden, and increase the current number of 1500 plants to 5000 in the next 2 years.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Please, do send me a good collection of your scrub seeds. The young Mr Fischers<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sons of Ludwig Fischer.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>can perhaps contribute a little to that as well. It will be in my power to make a large return gift.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">In true friendship</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Gossypium arboreum</p>
